	<li>Managing research data</li>&#13;
	<li>Doing research on iPhone and iPad</li>&#13;
	<li>Editing experiments</li>&#13;
	<li>Collaborating with colleagues</li>&#13;
	<li>Searching for results</li>&#13;
	<li>Staying up to date with the newsfeed</li>&#13;
	<li>Planning experiments with the calendar</li>&#13;
